info.author: Philippe Lagadec, Didier Stevens
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
pdfid_PL is a Python module to analyze and sanitize PDF files.
It is a slightly modified version of Didier Stevens' PDFiD, to be imported
in Python applications more easily.
See http://www.decalage.info/python/pdfid for more information.
info.name: pdfid_PL
info.summary: A Python module to analyze and sanitize PDF files, based on Didier Stevens' PDFiD
